---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-20" role="main">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p class="mb-6">Last updated: September 7, 2025</p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">We do not collect personal data from visitors to our website. Our website is a static informational site that does not require user registration or personal information submission.</p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Telegram Data</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Our services are provided through Telegram bots. Any data collected through our Telegram bots is subject to Telegram's privacy policy and terms of service. We only collect and process data necessary for the functionality of our bots.</p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Cookies and Tracking</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Our website does not use cookies or tracking technologies. We do not track visitors or collect browsing data.</p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Data Security</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">We implement appropriate security measures to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction of any data we may collect through our services.</p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.</p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us through our Telegram group.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>